sourcesContent:
<form nz-form [nzLayout]="'vertical'" [formGroup]="form" (ngSubmit)="onSubmit()"
  class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-2">
  <input formControlName="id" type="hidden" hidden>
  <nz-form-item>
    <nz-form-label nzRequired nzFor="firstName">{{'profile.firstName' | translate}}</nz-form-label>
    <nz-form-control nzErrorTip="The input is not valid First Name">
      <input nz-input formControlName="firstName" id="firstName" />
    </nz-form-control>
  </nz-form-item>
  <nz-form-item>
    <nz-form-label nzRequired nzFor="lastName">{{'profile.lastName' | translate}}</nz-form-label>
    <nz-form-control nzErrorTip="The input is not valid Last Name">
      <input nz-input formControlName="lastName" id="lastName" />
    </nz-form-control>
  </nz-form-item>
  <nz-form-item>
    <nz-form-label nzFor="mobileNumber" nzRequired>{{'profile.mobileNumber' | translate}}</nz-form-label>
    <nz-form-control nzErrorTip="The input is not valid Mobile Number">
      <input nz-input formControlName="mobileNumber" id="mobileNumber" />
    </nz-form-control>
  </nz-form-item>
  <nz-form-item>
    <nz-form-label nzFor="gender">{{'profile.gender' | translate}}</nz-form-label>
    <nz-form-control>
      <nz-select formControlName="gender">
        <nz-option nzLabel="Male" [nzValue]="gender.Male"></nz-option>
        <nz-option nzLabel="Female" [nzValue]="gender.Female"></nz-option>
      </nz-select>
    </nz-form-control>
  </nz-form-item>
  <nz-form-item>
    <nz-form-label nzFor="email" nzRequired>{{'profile.email' | translate}}</nz-form-label>
    <nz-form-control>
      <input nz-input formControlName="email" id="email" />
    </nz-form-control>
  </nz-form-item>
  <nz-form-item [hidden]="form.value.isResident == null">
    <nz-form-control>
      <label nz-checkbox id="isResident" formControlName="isResident">Is Resident?</label>
    </nz-form-control>
  </nz-form-item>
  <nz-form-item [hidden]="form.value.isResident == null">
    <nz-form-label nzFor="idNumber" nzRequired>ID Number</nz-form-label>
    <nz-form-control>
      <input nz-input formControlName="idNumber" id="idNumber" />
    </nz-form-control>
  </nz-form-item>
</form>
<button class="float-right" nz-button nzType="primary" [disabled]="form.invalid" (click)="onSubmit()">{{'profile.save' |
  translate}}</button>
